00:20:45,551 --> 00:20:49,592
So players understood that the robe and orb belonged to someone of low rank in the secret society,

525
00:20:49,832 --> 00:20:51,353
but there's a lot of confusion here,

526
00:20:52,033 --> 00:20:55,134
and I'd wanted it to be a cool reveal that Devi was in a secret society,

527
00:20:55,174 --> 00:20:55,754
but it wasn't.

528
00:20:56,234 --> 00:21:00,776
Like, who belonged to or knew about the secret society was an extremely messy topic for players.

