00:22:00,651 --> 00:22:03,953
which is normally hard to convey in environmental storytelling.

551
00:22:03,973 --> 00:22:06,093
And specifically he's descending into insanity.

552
00:22:08,312 --> 00:22:10,373
I was really excited to do an actual crime scene,

553
00:22:10,473 --> 00:22:11,593
but it didn't work that well.

554
00:22:12,173 --> 00:22:13,954
And it's because it's a nexus of a lot of the things

555
00:22:13,994 --> 00:22:15,975
that are hard to get right with environmental storytelling.

556
00:22:16,295 --> 00:22:18,096
So most people understand that T. Bryce

557
00:22:18,136 --> 00:22:20,276
escaped through the window and that L.S. was the victim.

558
00:22:20,857 --> 00:22:23,498
