00:22:26,259 --> 00:22:27,859
It's supposed to be the case that T. Bryce

561
00:22:27,939 --> 00:22:30,400
was fleeing from D.V. and he ran to his mother for help,

562
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:32,841
and then D.V. chased them both down to the basement,

563
00:22:32,861 --> 00:22:34,342
and then she helped her son escape,

564
00:22:34,402 --> 00:22:35,402
but she got caught instead.

565
00:22:36,075 --> 00:22:38,016
But that's a whole lot of stuff to try to fit together

566
00:22:38,036 --> 00:22:39,997
in a sequence, and people have other ideas,

567
00:22:40,037 --> 00:22:42,318
like well maybe LS was being held prisoner down here,

