00:24:47,885 --> 00:24:49,326
would have helped the player comprehension.

616
00:24:50,061 --> 00:24:52,362
And it takes a really long time to compare clues

617
00:24:52,782 --> 00:24:55,063
in both games, like, you know,

618
00:24:55,323 --> 00:24:56,583
if the clues are in separate levels,

619
00:24:57,163 --> 00:24:58,744
you can't just flip back and forth between them.

