00:25:25,531 --> 00:25:27,072
who you can examine really carefully

635
00:25:27,172 --> 00:25:30,094
and almost but not quite confirm that this is DV.

636
00:25:30,354 --> 00:25:32,835
But it can't be DV because DV is still alive.

637
00:25:32,875 --> 00:25:34,376
You've seen him in the window.

638
00:25:34,736 --> 00:25:37,118
He's up here with the kidnapped LS in the tower.

639
00:25:37,958 --> 00:25:38,779
So you make your way there,

640
00:25:39,199 --> 00:25:40,800
but when you arrive they are both gone.

