655
00:26:37,321 --> 00:26:38,181
right, in the Shrouded Moon,

656
00:26:38,562 --> 00:26:39,982
which is about mysteries and magic.

657
00:26:40,042 --> 00:26:41,383
What's real, what's not,

658
00:26:41,523 --> 00:26:42,684
and how you'd even know the difference,

