00:26:42,724 --> 00:26:44,765
which is something that I believe is very relevant today.

660
00:26:45,065 --> 00:26:46,766
There's plenty in the game that plays with this theme.

661
00:26:46,806 --> 00:26:49,487
There's the fate of LS, the quest for immortality.

